Code Here Now is a scrolling ticker of source code checkins made by people
recently at a specific place. It's good for hackathons, conferences, etc. It
also includes current local Twitter posts, Flickr photos, etc.

It's *very hacky* and *not finished* yet! Having said that, it's deployed at:

http://codeherenow.appspot.com/

Source: https://github.com/snarfed/codeherenow
Contact: Ryan Barrett <codeherenow@ryanb.org>

Code Here Now is in the public domain.
